{"experienceId":"draft-a1eb176e-db6a-4993-b330-95e3f94c5842","title":"外汇崩盘案例-委内瑞拉","contentVersion":"draft.acd6a12c49b0","mediaFingerprint":"sha256:acd6a12c49b0cf42af2537f515b9e66350fea3c5fa6726fccda426302637ee46","publishStatus":"draft","blockers":["HUMAN_REVIEW_REQUIRED"],"evidence":[{"evidenceId":"asr-73489d9140f9a89f","startMs":40,"endMs":2920,"text":"我们来看两个陷入危机导致外汇崩盘的国家。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-69a3956290f72d2b","startMs":4200,"endMs":7000,"text":"委内瑞拉，这可是全球石油储备最多的国家。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-7ce26ac5357d07d6","startMs":7040,"endMs":12040,"text":"可是呢，因为内部各种的政治原因，美国还对它制裁，持续20年严重的经济危机。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-95927b4a94719062","startMs":12160,"endMs":16040,"text":"就我感觉哈，危机这个词已经不足以形容委内瑞拉了，可能都太轻了。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-06d4a2f92cbd21a8","startMs":16080,"endMs":23800,"text":"据2021年的统计，委内瑞拉有94.5%的人生活在贫困线以下，有76.6%的人处于极度贫困，谋杀率世界第一。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-c4828daa0420ef5a","startMs":24910,"endMs":29310,"text":"你就看这么个政治动荡、经济危机的国家，你说它货币怎么可能好？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-b4734dac5bad3266","startMs":29310,"endMs":29550,"text":"对吧？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-4bd24531480880e1","startMs":29590,"endMs":41870,"text":"2010年的官方汇率是1美元兑2.15玻利瓦尔，2014年在黑市上是1美元兑100玻利瓦尔，2016年是3000， 2018年2月是2.5万，而到半年后，1美元就只能兑25万玻利瓦尔了。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-d56fd278241d3416","startMs":42050,"endMs":43010,"text":"而这都还是小波动。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-936673d5e9964897","startMs":43250,"endMs":46490,"text":"之后，委内瑞拉又经历了恶性的通货膨胀，这汇率就更止不住了。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88","startMs":46490,"endMs":54890,"text":"你看哈，这个是它对美元的汇率哈，注意这里边的纵轴，它是对数坐标，它是指数级往上蹿的，最后一美元已经能兑一万亿玻利瓦尔了。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-509aaf17107f031d","startMs":55470,"endMs":56670,"text":"我再给大家举个例子哈。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-02e28a1cd08d193b","startMs":56910,"endMs":60270,"text":"哎，我先考考你，你知道非洲最大的三个经济体是谁吗？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-4e97a76cda6c442d","startMs":60270,"endMs":62750,"text":"就是埃及、尼日利亚和南非。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-9aaf5df575e9e11d","startMs":63030,"endMs":64310,"text":"哎，我就想说这个尼日利亚。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-103b1f185ab28ad7","startMs":65610,"endMs":68010,"text":"他可是2亿多人口的大国，也闹幺蛾子。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-5229a639718dd4f9","startMs":68050,"endMs":71330,"text":"2022年的时候宣布说要重新设计他的大面额纸币。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-a37738c4ae255f91","startMs":71450,"endMs":74890,"text":"哎，两个月以后哈，原来旧的那些钱就全作废了，你们赶紧去银行换新的。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-c125a09ec151dbfd","startMs":74890,"endMs":76170,"text":"大家一下就慌了呀，对吧？"},{"evidenceId":"asr-798e372c538b4437","startMs":76210,"endMs":78490,"text":"干什么活啊，赶紧去银行排队等着换钱吧！"},{"evidenceId":"asr-5c8372de6d1f45a7","startMs":78920,"endMs":83760,"text":"哎，看过咱们之前聊印度经济的朋友哈，可能还记得印度它在2016年的时候就也干过类似的事。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-633ae8c438b14cc0","startMs":83840,"endMs":86920,"text":"这么做的原因呢，主要是为了遏制黑市啊，反腐败啊等等。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-ced3a90884030aac","startMs":86960,"endMs":93480,"text":"但是它短期内对经济的打击实在是太大了，尤其是你看尼日利亚又在一个全球性通货膨胀、能源危机的时候，整这么一出。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2","startMs":93560,"endMs":100480,"text":"他还取消了燃油补贴，就导致尼日利亚奈拉持续崩盘，这反过来又加速了他们国内的通货膨胀，现在已经超过了30%。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-52ce0c3971860ef0","startMs":100560,"endMs":102360,"text":"国内也开始出现大规模的罢工。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-63eb86f89d03a335","startMs":102600,"endMs":105560,"text":"你看啊，这个也是一个陷入危机导致货币下跌的例子。"},{"evidenceId":"asr-d90c11bc85233e81","startMs":105600,"endMs":109800,"text":"其实最近类似的像阿根廷、埃及、斯里兰卡等等，类似的例子其实非常多。"}],"concepts":[{"conceptId":"C1","name":"Currency Collapse (外汇崩盘)","firstMentionMs":40,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-73489d9140f9a89f"]},{"conceptId":"C2","name":"Venezuela Country Profile (委内瑞拉:全球最大石油储备国)","firstMentionMs":4200,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-69a3956290f72d2b"]},{"conceptId":"C3","name":"US Sanctions on Venezuela (美国制裁,持续20年)","firstMentionMs":7040,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-7ce26ac5357d07d6"]},{"conceptId":"C4","name":"Venezuela Political Turmoil & Economic Crisis (政治动荡与严重经济危机)","firstMentionMs":7040,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-7ce26ac5357d07d6","asr-c4828daa0420ef5a"]},{"conceptId":"C5","name":"Venezuelan Poverty Statistics (2021)","firstMentionMs":16080,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-06d4a2f92cbd21a8"]},{"conceptId":"C6","name":"Bolívar (VES) Exchange Rate Timeline","firstMentionMs":29590,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-4bd24531480880e1"]},{"conceptId":"C7","name":"Black-Market vs Official Exchange Rate Gap (黑市汇率 vs 官方汇率)","firstMentionMs":29590,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-4bd24531480880e1","asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]},{"conceptId":"C8","name":"Hyperinflation (恶性通货膨胀)","firstMentionMs":43250,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-936673d5e9964897"]},{"conceptId":"C9","name":"Largest African Economies (埃及、尼日利亚、南非)","firstMentionMs":56910,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-02e28a1cd08d193b","asr-4e97a76cda6c442d"]},{"conceptId":"C10","name":"Nigeria: 200M+ Population Large Country (2亿多人口大国)","firstMentionMs":65610,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-103b1f185ab28ad7"]},{"conceptId":"C11","name":"Naira Currency Redenomination (2022重新设计大面额纸币)","firstMentionMs":68050,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-5229a639718dd4f9"]},{"conceptId":"C12","name":"Sudden Demonetization (旧钞票两个月内作废)","firstMentionMs":71450,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-a37738c4ae255f91"]},{"conceptId":"C13","name":"Bank-Run Panic Queueing (银行排队挤兑)","firstMentionMs":76210,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-798e372c538b4437"]},{"conceptId":"C14","name":"Stated Rationale: 遏制黑市、反腐败","firstMentionMs":83840,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-633ae8c438b14cc0"]},{"conceptId":"C15","name":"Global Inflation & Energy Crisis Backdrop (全球性通货膨胀、能源危机)","firstMentionMs":86960,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-ced3a90884030aac"]},{"conceptId":"C16","name":"Fuel Subsidy Removal (取消燃油补贴)","firstMentionMs":93560,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"conceptId":"C17","name":"Naira Persistent Collapse (奈拉持续崩盘)","firstMentionMs":93560,"isCore":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"conceptId":"C18","name":"Domestic Inflation Above 30%","firstMentionMs":93560,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"conceptId":"C19","name":"Large-Scale Domestic Strikes (大规模罢工)","firstMentionMs":100560,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-52ce0c3971860ef0"]},{"conceptId":"C20","name":"Other Similar Cases: Argentina, Egypt, Sri Lanka","firstMentionMs":105600,"isCore":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-d90c11bc85233e81"]}],"claims":[{"claimId":"CL1","statement":"委内瑞拉虽是全球石油储备最多的国家,但因内部政治原因和美国长达20年的制裁,陷入严重经济危机。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-69a3956290f72d2b","asr-7ce26ac5357d07d6"]},{"claimId":"CL2","statement":"据2021年统计,委内瑞拉有94.5%的人口生活在贫困线以下,76.6%处于极度贫困,且该国谋杀率为世界第一。","assetClass":null,"assertedDirection":"insufficient","evidenceIds":["asr-06d4a2f92cbd21a8"]},{"claimId":"CL3","statement":"在视频描述的政治动荡与经济危机背景下,玻利瓦尔面临明显的下行压力","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-c4828daa0420ef5a","asr-b4734dac5bad3266"]},{"claimId":"CL4","statement":"玻利瓦尔兑美元汇率从2010年官方1 USD = 2.15 VES,到2014年黑市100 VES、2016年3000 VES、2018年2月2.5万 VES,半年后达25万 VES,最终因恶性通胀飙升至1 USD ≈ 1万亿 VES(对数坐标上呈指数级上升)。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-4bd24531480880e1","asr-936673d5e9964897","asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]},{"claimId":"CL5","statement":"委内瑞拉官方汇率与黑市汇率在叙述中被并列提及,两者均呈上升趋势且差距持续扩大","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-4bd24531480880e1","asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]},{"claimId":"CL6","statement":"尼日利亚(2亿多人口大国)在2022年宣布重新设计大面额纸币,两个月后旧钞票作废引发民众恐慌、银行挤兑。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-5229a639718dd4f9","asr-a37738c4ae255f91","asr-c125a09ec151dbfd","asr-798e372c538b4437"]},{"claimId":"CL7","statement":"纸币重新设计的官方动机被表述为遏制黑市与反腐败,但短期内对经济冲击巨大。","assetClass":null,"assertedDirection":"conflict","evidenceIds":["asr-633ae8c438b14cc0","asr-ced3a90884030aac"]},{"claimId":"CL8","statement":"在全球性通货膨胀与能源危机叠加的背景下,尼日利亚同时推进纸币改革,放大了短期经济冲击。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-ced3a90884030aac"]},{"claimId":"CL9","statement":"尼日利亚取消燃油补贴,推动奈拉持续崩盘;奈拉贬值又反过来加速国内通货膨胀,通胀率已超过30%。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"claimId":"CL10","statement":"经济压力传导至社会层面,尼日利亚国内出现大规模罢工。","assetClass":null,"assertedDirection":"pressure_dominant","evidenceIds":["asr-52ce0c3971860ef0"]},{"claimId":"CL11","statement":"近期类似的\"陷入危机导致货币下跌\"的例子还包括阿根廷、埃及、斯里兰卡等。","assetClass":"fx","assertedDirection":"insufficient","evidenceIds":["asr-d90c11bc85233e81"]}],"causalEdges":[{"edgeId":"E1","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C3"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C4"},"mechanism":"内部政治原因叠加长达20年的美国制裁,共同构成外部压力并放大内部矛盾,从而形成持续性的经济危机。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-7ce26ac5357d07d6"]},{"edgeId":"E2","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C-VE-Crisis"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL3"},"mechanism":"在视频叙述中,玻利瓦尔被置于'政治动荡与经济危机'的语境下,说话者以反问句式对其表现前景提出方向性质疑","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-c4828daa0420ef5a","asr-b4734dac5bad3266"]},{"edgeId":"E3","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C4"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C8"},"mechanism":"持续的经济危机破坏生产、供给与货币流通体系,最终触发恶性通货膨胀。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-936673d5e9964897"]},{"edgeId":"E4","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C8"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL4"},"mechanism":"恶性通胀使本币购买力沿对数坐标指数级崩塌,玻利瓦尔兑美元最终需要1万亿单位才能兑1美元。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]},{"edgeId":"E5","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C-VE-RateDivergence"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL5"},"mechanism":"通过并列引用官方汇率与黑市汇率的时间序列数据,展示两套汇率均呈上升趋势且差距随时间显著拉大","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-4bd24531480880e1","asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]},{"edgeId":"E6","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C11"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C12"},"mechanism":"宣布重新设计大面额纸币后,政府设定2个月窗口期让旧钞作废,直接触发突然性货币替换。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-5229a639718dd4f9","asr-a37738c4ae255f91"]},{"edgeId":"E7","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C12"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C13"},"mechanism":"突然作废旧钞使存量现金失去价值,公众为避免损失集中前往银行兑换新钞,形成挤兑压力。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-c125a09ec151dbfd","asr-798e372c538b4437"]},{"edgeId":"E8","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C11"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL7"},"mechanism":"官方声称政策目的是打击黑市与腐败,但短期内对实体经济运行的冲击可能盖过其执法收益。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-633ae8c438b14cc0","asr-ced3a90884030aac"]},{"edgeId":"E9","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C15"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL8"},"mechanism":"全球通胀与能源危机本已推高尼日利亚进口与生产成本,叠加纸币改革带来的流动性冲击,形成共振性的短期经济打击。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-ced3a90884030aac"]},{"edgeId":"E10","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C16"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C17"},"mechanism":"取消燃油补贴抬升能源与运输成本,削弱经常账户和外汇储备,推动本币持续走弱。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"edgeId":"E11","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C17"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C18"},"mechanism":"奈拉贬值抬升进口商品价格,反过来通过输入性渠道加速国内通胀(已超过30%)。","omittedIntermediate":false,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"edgeId":"E12","from":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C-NG-CurrencyCollapse"},"to":{"nodeType":"concept","nodeId":"C-NG-Strikes"},"mechanism":"在视频叙述中,货币崩盘与通胀加速的背景被直接关联到国内出现的大规模罢工","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2","asr-52ce0c3971860ef0"]},{"edgeId":"E13","from":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL4"},"to":{"nodeType":"claim","nodeId":"CL11"},"mechanism":"将委内瑞拉与尼日利亚作为案例后,类比延伸到阿根廷、埃及、斯里兰卡,构成\"危机导致货币下跌\"的多国样本。","omittedIntermediate":true,"evidenceIds":["asr-d90c11bc85233e81","asr-63eb86f89d03a335"]}],"conditions":[{"conditionId":"CD1","variable":"Nigeria_inflation_rate","operator":"above","threshold":30,"unit":"%","statement":"尼日利亚国内通胀率已经超过30%","evidenceIds":["asr-85f4f04fe83c0fb2"]},{"conditionId":"CD2","variable":"old_banknote_validity","operator":"below","threshold":60,"unit":"days","affectsEdgeId":"E7","statement":"旧钞在不到2个月的窗口期后被宣告作废,该短期过渡窗口触发了银行挤兑行为。","evidenceIds":["asr-a37738c4ae255f91","asr-798e372c538b4437"]},{"conditionId":"CD3","variable":"Venezuela_USD_VES_exchange_rate_log_trend","operator":"above","threshold":0,"unit":"log_units","statement":"玻利瓦尔兑美元汇率在对数坐标轴上呈持续上升(贬值)趋势","evidenceIds":["asr-0a05c7e5c4377f88"]}],"triggerCandidates":[],"rejectedTriggerCandidates":[{"candidateId":"cue-EV9","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV5","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV8","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV3","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV4","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV11","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV2","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV12","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV1","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV7","reason":"MIN_GAP_VIOLATION"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV6","reason":"PAYLOAD_UNAUTHORABLE"},{"candidateId":"cue-EV10","reason":"PAYLOAD_UNAUTHORABLE"}],"approvedTriggers":[]}